# ⚡ PowerDeck — System Control GUI

A sleek and modern **Python Tkinter app** that lets you easily **Restart, Log Out, or Shut Down** your computer with a single click.

![PowerDeck Screenshot](https://github.com/yourusername/pyverse/assets/yourimageid/powerdeck-ui.png)

---

## 🌟 Features
- 🔁 **Restart** your system instantly  
- ⏱️ **Restart (20s delay)** option  
- 🔒 **Log Out** with one click  
- ⏻ **Shut Down** safely  
- 💎 Modern dark UI with square cards and hover effects  
- 🖋️ Sleek typography and icon-based design  

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack
- **Python 3**
- **Tkinter** (for GUI)
- **os module** (for system commands)

